Test Case 7 — Attendee with no suggestions within 2-4 degrees (Liam Byrne, ID 102)
Context: ID 102 is connected only to 110 (Cian Roche), who has no onward connections within 4 degrees

Input: Attendee ID 102

Expected: No suggestions available (no suitable connections found within 2–4 degrees)

Step 3 — Verify in Neo4j Browser
Execute the following Cypher query to verify results:

MATCH path = (a:Attendee {AttendeeID: 101})-[:CONNECTED_TO*2..4]-(s:Attendee)
WHERE NOT (a)-[:CONNECTED_TO]-(s) AND s.AttendeeID <> 101
RETURN s.AttendeeID AS suggested, MIN(length(path)) AS degrees
ORDER BY degrees

Confirm returned IDs match: 103, 115, 120, 106, 104, 114

